- content_for :page_title, "Now check your email"
.attention
  %h3= yield :page_title
  %p
    Shortly you should receive an email from PlanningAlerts.org.au.
    %span.highlight Click on the link in the email
    to confirm your comment.
    Your comment will not be displayed or sent to
    = @comment&.recipient_display_name
    until you click on the link in the email.
  %p
    If you don't get an email in the next few minutes, try checking your spam filter.
